data.description: Welcome to this charming brick home located in the desirable neighborhood of NRH. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, this residence offers ample space for you and your family. The recent updates include a new roof, windows, air conditioner, and an updated kitchen, ensuring a comfortable and modern living experience. The back yard is perfect for kids or pets to enjoy with its generous size. I'm thrilled to let you know that the swing set and trampoline will convey with the property if you would like. This means that you'll have even more options for outdoor play and entertainment right in your own backyard. It's the perfect setup for creating lasting memories with your family. This home exudes character with its unique features and design elements. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your own - schedule a showing today!
